This is the list of file to modify for the Tlee plots

file_ch.txt 	---> Pool of available files (specify breakdown of each file)
cv_input.txt	---> Files to used with POT for each included sample
cov_input.txt	---> Variables to plot, samples to consider, histogram configurations

det_file.txt	---> Useful for merging
det_file_ch.txt ---> Pool of available files 
det_input.txt	---> Specify input and output files with POT normalization

xf_file_ch.txt	---> Pool of available files 
xf_input.txt	---> Specify input and output files with POT normalization

wcp-uboone-bdt/inc/WCPLEEANA/Configure_Lee.h ---> Specify number of channels and some settings
wcp-uboone-bdt/srcs/TLee.cxx ---> Specify name of channels

wcp-uboone-bdt/inc/WCPLEEANA/cuts.h 	---> List of all cuts, for variables and histograms

wcp-uboone-bdt/apps/det_cov_matrix.cxx 	---> Script for ./run_det_sys.pl
wcp-uboone-bdt/apps/xf_cov_matrix.cxx 	---> Script for ./run_xf_sys.pl
wcp-uboone-bdt/apps/read_TLee_v20.cxx 	---> Script for ./bin/read_TLee_v20
wcp-uboone-bdt/apps/plot_hist.cxx 		---> Script for ./bin/plot_hist -r0 -l0 -e3 -sfile_collapsed_covariance_matrix.root